20名埃及部落客搭乘火車前往[科普特屠殺](https://globalvoicesonline.org/2010/01/08/egypt-naga-
hammady-massacre/ "https://globalvoicesonline.org/2010/01/08/egypt-naga-
hammady-massacre/")的事發地[Naga
Hammady](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nag_Hammadi/
"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nag_Hammadi/")，[抵達後即遭逮捕](https://globalvoicesonline.org/2010/01/15/egypt-
bloggers-arrested-over-naga-hammady-massacre/
"https://globalvoicesonline.org/2010/01/15/egypt-bloggers-arrested-over-naga-
hammady-
massacre/")。為了捍衛他們的發言權，埃及的部落客和行動主義者在1月22日召開討論會。在旋即被釋放之後，他們向大家[說明](https://globalvoicesonline.org/2010/01/20/egypt-
detained-bloggers-tell-their-tales/
"https://globalvoicesonline.org/2010/01/20/egypt-detained-bloggers-tell-their-
tales/")自己是如何被有關當局「劫持」，不准他們向受害者家屬致意。

